    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-03-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-03-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="533"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d533">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Fallières</persName> to
                        President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-03-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 13, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The sympathy so cordially expressed by you in the name of your Government and of
                    the United States nation for the families of the victims of the terrible
                    catastrophe of Courrieres touches me very sincerely, and in the name of the
                    Government of the Republic I express to you my very deep gratitude.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">A. Fallières.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
